    <title></title>
    <link href="/2022/03/18/Time%20Series%20Anomaly%20Detection%20with%20Multiresolution%20Ensemble%20Decoding/"/>
    <url>/2022/03/18/Time%20Series%20Anomaly%20Detection%20with%20Multiresolution%20Ensemble%20Decoding/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Time-Series-Anomaly-Detection-with-Multiresolution-Ensemble-Decoding"><a href="#Time-Series-Anomaly-Detection-with-Multiresolution-Ensemble-Decoding" class="headerlink" title="Time Series Anomaly Detection with Multiresolution Ensemble Decoding"></a>Time Series Anomaly Detection with Multiresolution Ensemble Decoding</h1><blockquote><p>The Thirty-Fifth AAAI Conference on Artificial Intelligence (AAAI-21)</p></blockquote><p><a href="https://ojs.aaai.org/index.php/AAAI/article/view/17152">Time Series Anomaly Detection with Multiresolution Ensemble Decoding</a></p><h2 id="Introduction"><a href="#Introduction" class="headerlink" title="Introduction"></a>Introduction</h2><p>循环自编码器是一种在时间序列异常检测上的常用模型，通过重构误差来区别极端值或者异常值。但是目前的循环自编码器仍然存在着过拟合、错误累积的问题。这篇文章提出了 <code>Recurrent Autoencoder with Multiresolution Ensemble Decoding (RAMED)</code> 集成多分辨率解码器的循环自编码器。通过不同长度的解码器以及一种从粗到细的机制，让较低分辨率的解码器产生的信息帮助较高分辨率的解码器输出信息。同时本文用一种多分辨率形状强制损失(multiresolution shape-forcing loss)让不同分辨率输出的不同长度的信息来匹配输入的全局信息。最后通过最下层的解码器也就是分辨率最高的解码器来计算异常分数。</p><h2 id="Method"><a href="#Method" class="headerlink" title="Method"></a>Method</h2><p>整体框架可以分为编码器部分，解码器部分，mse loss，multiresolution shape-forcing loss</p><p>![framework](.\Time Series Anomaly Detection with Multiresolution Ensemble Decoding.assets\image-20220318160719122.png)</p><h3 id="Encoder-Decoder-Ensemble"><a href="#Encoder-Decoder-Ensemble" class="headerlink" title="Encoder-Decoder Ensemble"></a>Encoder-Decoder Ensemble</h3><h4 id="Encoder"><a href="#Encoder" class="headerlink" title="Encoder"></a>Encoder</h4><p>编码器部分由多个编码器同时对数据进行编码，编码器部分由多个LSTM单元组成，一般的RNN的输出由当前时刻的输入与前一个RNN单元输出的隐藏层共同决定：</p><p>![LSTM-base](..\img\Time Series Anomaly Detection with Multiresolution Ensemble Decoding.assets\image-20220318161815954.png)</p><p>在这篇文章中使用了 <a href="https://www.ijcai.org/Proceedings/2019/0378.pdf">IJCAI 2019 ：Outlier Detection for Time Series with Recurrent Autoencoder</a>在RNN单元中增加了稀疏的跳连接，计算方式如下：</p><p>![LSTM-skip](.\Time Series Anomaly Detection with Multiresolution Ensemble Decoding.assets\image-20220318162258814.png)</p><p><code>w1,w2</code>的值从<code>&#123;(1,0),(0,1),(1,1)&#125;</code>中随机采样，s表示加入前s个RNN单元输出的隐藏层。</p><p>这样每一个编码器讲输入编码为$h_{T}^{(E_i)}$ ,然后将所有编码器编码后的结果拼接在一起，再通过一个多层感知机将形状变化为一个编码器编码后的向量形状：</p><p>![encode-concat](..\img\Time Series Anomaly Detection with Multiresolution Ensemble Decoding.assets\image-20220318162822277.png)</p><h4 id="Decoder"><a href="#Decoder" class="headerlink" title="Decoder"></a>Decoder</h4><p>将$h^{(E)}$作为解码器的初始状态，则第k个解码器的输出${y_{T}^{k},…,y_{1}^{k}}$和隐藏状态${h_{T-  1},…,h_{1}}$通过如下方式计算：</p><p>![lstm](..\img\Time Series Anomaly Detection with Multiresolution Ensemble Decoding.assets\image-20220318163532823.png)</p><p>可以看到解码器的输出序列和编码器的输入序列是相反的。</p><h3 id="Multiresolution-Ensemble-Decoding"><a href="#Multiresolution-Ensemble-Decoding" class="headerlink" title="Multiresolution Ensemble Decoding"></a>Multiresolution Ensemble Decoding</h3><p>本文提出的模型集成了多分辨率的解码器，就是对于不同的解码器它的解码长度不相等，解码长度比较短的解码器可以捕获宏观的时序特征，比较长的解码器可以更为详细的时间序列特征。之后通过多分辨率的融合策略完成从粗到细的融合过程。为了让解码器的输出和输入的数据相似，采用了基于DTW的损失，比较长度不一样的输出输入序列的相似性。</p><h3 id="Decoder-Lengths"><a href="#Decoder-Lengths" class="headerlink" title="Decoder Lengths"></a>Decoder Lengths</h3><p>第<code>k</code>个解码器的重构时间序列$T_{k}$的长度满足如下公式<br>$$<br>T_{k}=\alpha_{k}T \ \alpha_k = 1 / \tau^{k - 1} \in(0,1])<br>$$<br>将<code>k = 1</code>带入公式中可以发现，第一个解码器也就是最下面的解码器输出序列的长度和输入序列的长度是一样的，这里$\tau = 2$所以相邻两个编码器下面的编码器长度是上面的编码器长度的两倍。最上层的解码器长度至少为2。</p><h3 id="Coarse-to-Fine-Fusion"><a href="#Coarse-to-Fine-Fusion" class="headerlink" title="Coarse-to-Fine Fusion"></a><strong>Coarse-to-Fine Fusion</strong></h3><p>因为不同编码器的输出长度不一样，所以不能直接采用均值或者中位数的方式来融合，这里采用了一种从粗到细的融合策略对于两个编码器$D^{k}$和$D^{k + 1}$,这里$D^{k} &gt; D^{k + 1}$,所以解码器$D^{k + 1}$的粒度更粗，除了最上层的解码器外，其他的每个解码器将之前的隐藏状态$h_{t + 1}^{k}$与来自$D^{k + 1}$个解码器的$h_{\lceil t/ \tau \rceil}^{k+1}$混合，通过MLP恢复为原来的形状：</p><p>![decode-concat](..\img\Time Series Anomaly Detection with Multiresolution Ensemble Decoding.assets\image-20220318170313758.png)</p><p>解码器的LSTM还加入的噪声：</p><p>![decode-lstm](..\img\Time Series Anomaly Detection with Multiresolution Ensemble Decoding.assets\image-20220318170416309.png)</p><p>最后我们最下层的解码器的输出为:$Y_{recon} = [y_1^{(1)},y_2^{(1)},…,y_T^{(1)}]$和输入序列的长度一样，我们用MSE来计算重构误差：![mse](.\Time Series Anomaly Detection with Multiresolution Ensemble Decoding.assets\image-20220318170616771.png)</p><h3 id="Multiresolution-Shape-Forcing-Loss"><a href="#Multiresolution-Shape-Forcing-Loss" class="headerlink" title="Multiresolution Shape-Forcing Loss"></a>Multiresolution Shape-Forcing Loss</h3><p>在解码器中只有最下面解码器输出的序列长度和输入一样，其他的解码器输出长度都小于输入。为了进一步鼓励解码器学习不同分辨率下的一致时间模式，这里使用了基于DTW的损失。</p><h4 id="DTW"><a href="#DTW" class="headerlink" title="DTW"></a>DTW</h4><p><a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/43247215">DTW介绍</a></p><p>我们可以发现DTW中存在min操作所以是不可微的，这里采用了sDTW：</p><p>![sdtw](..\img\Time Series Anomaly Detection with Multiresolution Ensemble Decoding.assets\image-20220318170939441.png)</p><p>基于sDTW的损失为：</p><p>![sdtw-loss](..\img\Time Series Anomaly Detection with Multiresolution Ensemble Decoding.assets\image-20220318171007485.png)</p><p>最终损失为：</p><p>![all-loss](..\img\Time Series Anomaly Detection with Multiresolution Ensemble Decoding.assets\image-20220318171020769.png)</p><h3 id="Anomaly-Score-and-Detection"><a href="#Anomaly-Score-and-Detection" class="headerlink" title="Anomaly Score and Detection"></a>Anomaly Score and Detection</h3><p>对于输入$X$和重构后的$Y$，计算出每一个时刻的误差$e(t)$，使用验证机中的所有$e(t)$，来拟合一个正太分布$N(\mu,\sum)$，推理阶段，判断序列异常的概率为：</p><p>![pro](..\img\Time Series Anomaly Detection with Multiresolution Ensemble Decoding.assets\image-20220318171819234.png)</p><p>异常分数为：</p><p>![score](..\img\Time Series Anomaly Detection with Multiresolution Ensemble Decoding.assets\image-20220318171845333.png)</p><h2 id="Summary"><a href="#Summary" class="headerlink" title="Summary"></a>Summary</h2><p>这篇文章基于RAE-ensemble，集成了多个编码器和解码器，解码器中采用了从粗到细的机制，这里对于不同的解码器采用不同的损失函数。计算异常分数时，首先用验证集拟合一个正太分布，测试时如果误差偏离正太分布一定阈值，判定为异常</p>]]></content>
    
    
    
